This paper discusses the application of Nesterov's accelerated gradient methods in machine learning, specifically in training max-margin models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of these methods in computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The paper also discusses the optimization of models, which could fall under the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
